{"word":"G2554 - κακοποιέω - kakopoiéō - kak-op-oy-eh'-o - Do evil","slug":"G2554","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακοποιέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kakopoiéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kak-op-oy-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Do evil"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - kakopoieo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kak-op-oy-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2555\">G2555</a>; to <i>be a bad doer</i>, that is, (objectively) to <i>injure</i>, or (generally) to <i>sin:</i> - do (-ing) evil."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420\">G420</a>"}]}